    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The acid-resistant substance used for aquatint, made by dusting rosin particles onto a plate and heating.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
